description: T’is the season for Christmas trees and we have the perfect Mini Christmas Tree with Lights right here. Anyone is sure to fall in love with our real mini Picea tree. It comes fully decorated with LED fairy lights. Definitely the best tree gift by far to send this season, nothing else is more fitting of the celebrations. Perfect to send as an early Christmas gift or to simply decorate your house ready for the celebrations. The tree is planted in a 19cm growing pot and arrives with a rustic style outer hessian pot. Keep roots moist but not wet and when the festivities have finished you can remove the decor and the tree will thrive through the new coming year and even longer. * The mini Christmas tree is a Picea variety * An ideal early Christmas gift or to brighten up an apartment or office * Arrives decorated with LED fairy lights and baubles * Delivered in a 1.5ltr growing pot with a rustic hessian outer pot * Tree arrives 40cm-50cm in height * Batteries included with fairy lights Interested in buying these in bulk for your office?
